Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 podman, gocryptfs, fuse3, fuse-overlayfs, slirp4netns,
 openssh-client, openssh-server, util-linux, skopeo,
 qemu-system-x86, qemu-utils, virtiofsd,
 libvirt-daemon-system, libvirt-clients,
 libarchive-tools, iproute2, xorriso, genisoimage, ovmf,
 dnsmasq-base, swtpm, gnupg, pinentry-curses
Suggests: docker.io, cloudflared, gvisor-tap-vsock, nvidia-driver, kubectl
Description: Overthink container management CLI
 Compose, build, deploy, and manage container boxes from a library of fully
 configurable candies. Ships the ov binary; apt auto-resolves its mandatory
 dependencies. Tailscale is NOT a dependency here (it is not in Debian main) —
 the ov layer supplies tailscale for Debian/Ubuntu via the tailscale apt repo.
